-- Switzerland Sees Enormous Inflows on Euro-Zone Concern, NZZ Says
-- B y   S i m e o n   B e n n e t t
-- 2012-05-20T11:01:40Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-05-20/switzerland-sees-enormous-inflows-on-euro-zone-concern-nzz-says.html
Switzerland is seeing “enormous”
investment inflows because of increasing concern about the
future of the euro zone,  NZZ am Sonntag  reported, citing an
unidentified major business partner of  UBS AG. (UBSN)   Swiss financial market inflows were as much as four times
higher than normal on some days during the past week, the Swiss
newspaper reported.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Simeon Bennett in Geneva at 
